  06 Oct 2003; David Holm <dholm@gentoo.org> florist-3.15p.ebuild:
  Moved to stable on x86.

  19 Sep 2003; David Holm <dholm@gentoo.org> florist-3.15p.ebuild:
  Added to ~ppc.

  17 Aug 2003; David Holm <dholm@gentoo.org> metadata.xml:
  Added metadata.xml.

